<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Book Details</title>
    <style>
        .container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .image {
            max-height: 100%;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }
        table {
            width: 50%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: auto;
        }
        th, td {
            border: 1px solid black;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            width: 30%;
        }
        td {
            width: 70%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Chi tiết sách</h1>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="your-image-source.jpg" alt="Book Image" class="image">
        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>Tên sách</th>
                <td>{{result.Title}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Tác giả</th>
                <td>{{result.Author}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Nhà xuất bản</th>
                <td>{{result.Publisher}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Giá</th>
                <td>{{result.Price}} VNĐ</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Số lượng</th>
                <td>{{result.Quantity}}</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
    <h3>Mô tả chi tiết</h3>
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Expedita possimus deleniti repudiandae aspernatur porro quibusdam natus ut atque, quia magnam animi quisquam enim eveniet sapiente delectus quis exercitationem commodi voluptas?</p>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
        <a href="/home" class="my-2 py-2 btn btn-primary">Quay lại</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
